<chapter line="1">Vejjācariya kaṇḍa</chapter>
<hangnum line="2" number="286"></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="3">Āyubedakatābhyāso <pageBreak edition="M" number="0.0173" />, sabbesaṃ piyadassano;</gatha1>
<gathalast line="4">Ariyasīlaguṇopeto, esa vejjo vidhīyate.</gathalast>
<hangnum line="5" number="287"></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="6">Nānāganthajānanañca, sudiṭṭhakammasampadā;</gatha1>
<gathalast line="7">Dakkhatā hatthasīghatā, pasādasūrasattitā.</gathalast>
<hangnum line="8" number="288"></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="9">Sābhāvikataṅkhaṇika-ñāṇasubhāsitāpi ca;</gatha1>
<gathalast line="10">Ussāho dabbo sabbatā, vejjācerassa lakkhaṇaṃ;</gathalast>
<hangnum line="11" number="289"></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="12">Kiliṭṭhavatthaṃ <pageBreak edition="M" number="0.0174" />kodho ca, atimānañca gammatā;</gatha1>
<gathalast line="13">Animantitagamanaṃ, ete pañca vivajjiyā.</gathalast>
<hangnum line="14" number="290"></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="15">Diṭṭhakammatā <pageBreak edition="M" number="0.0175" />socañca, dakkhatā viditāgamo;</gatha1>
<gathalast line="16">Cattāro subhisakkassa, suguṇā viññunā matā.</gathalast>
<hangnum line="17" number="291"></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="18">Rujāya jayalakkhaṇaṃ, raso ca bhesajjampi ca;</gatha1>
<gathalast line="19">Tilakkhaṇabhedo ceva, viññeyyo bhisakkena ve.</gathalast>
